{"tid":1189361,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"睇網典原來2012年前已經開始睇達哥","createTime":"2019-06-06T18:12:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-06T18:23:22.000Z","uid":154935,"like":12,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e711f4474cbe197004ed5edf25b80f71913b0bbb","tid":1189361,"uid":154935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T18:12:25.000Z","msg":"見到有達哥fans 打句係真兄弟就會明<br />\n又話睇達哥睇咗好多年,達哥台係打機台唔係政治台, 唔支持達哥嘅唔係真兄弟<br />\n有哋人問點解會迫達哥表態但又唔迫其他名人,例如黃子華<br />\n我自己就覺得係因為達哥係我心目中係企係人民嘅一邊,同其他名人係唔同,但估唔到佢都會有一日選擇沉默<br />\n唔知你哋有冇睇過下面條片<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-87VW_BpBto\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D-87VW_BpBto&d=KA2pTlu%2BoVpRwWZcRxs8e%2FSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=57370f5b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-87VW_BpBto</a><br />\n我自己對條片都幾深刻,其實仲有好多類似嘅言論佢玩fifa都會講,所以達哥嘅台喺我心目中唔只係打機,仲會講好多道理,教你點樣做人<br />\n不過估唔到今年會對64隻字不提,所以其實都幾失望<br />\n可能真係要身無牽掛先可以為人仗義<br />\n我就唔支持迫人表態,亦都冇去迫佢表態,其實佢嘅行為已經表達咗"},{"pid":"31700a2feca451525ddecb257a27b49dd956a8e8","tid":1189361,"uid":40628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T18:12:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WmY1Du8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWmY1Du8.jpg&h=6ddcf26c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f07d7010847e63f470e6acc9fe3d935a49f79f51","tid":1189361,"uid":154935,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T18:19:59.000Z","msg":"仲有就係希望支持達哥沉默嘅人唔係因為咁而反對69遊行<br />\n見到有人覺得睇直播仲重要過香港嘅未來真係幾慘<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SNRN6c7.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSNRN6c7.gif&h=fb18a5cd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0820cf768ea025a97090042b31affbe3ca9045fa","tid":1189361,"uid":912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T18:23:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />ok<br />\n69記得出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"h